Please look at the issue template:

(https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/new)

It's not clear that your problem is a bug, rather than a question about proper usage. If it's a question about usage, it should be posted to stackoverflow.

If you think it's a bug, please provide all of the information requested in the issue template.
